data.description: ENTERTAINER'S GORGEOUS RESORT STYLE HOME WITH RARE OPPORUNITY TO HAVE A PRIVATE POOL AND ABSOLUTELY AMAZING SUNSET VIEWS. This home has been extremely well cared for with updates to include new windows, new front door, updated flooring in the office and great room.  Garage has built-in cabinets and utility sink as well as epoxy flooring. Be prepared to be impressed with the amenities this home has to offer.  Expense was not spared with the beautiful backyard, a staycation paradise.  Spacious master bedroom, generous size bathroom with grey tone vanity and chic carpeting.  French doors lead to game/TV room which could easily be used as a 4th bedroom. This home is absolutely MOVE-IN READY.  Cobblestone Farms is a beautiful planned community with well-maintained landscaping & community parks.
